  "keyFeatures": [
    "Async-first design built on asyncio",
    "REST API client with automatic rate limiting",
    "WebSocket gateway for real-time events",
    "Decorator-based command framework",
    "Modular cog system for organizing code",
    "Optional voice support with LiveKit",
    "Strongly-typed data models",
    "Clean separation between low-level Client and high-level Bot"
